From 08be99a223ff51bdf42e9bd26c56f5886446b54b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jeroen Wijenbergh <jeroen.wijenbergh@geant.org>
Date: Tue, 12 Aug 2025 13:48:30 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Changes for puregotk

- change module name to jwijenbergh/purego
- add support for []string as return kind
- add support for arrays by converting them to slices
- add support for deduplicating callbacks via function ptr (more info,
  see: https://github.com/jwijenbergh/purego/pull/1)
- add support for strings in callback arguments
- convert []string->**byte
- return if too many arguments instead of panicking
